                0.475,
                0.871,
                0.509
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "To balance in EUR the relation 'Opening + Sum of flows = Closing' for each line, we need to introduce a \"Translation adjustment\" flow."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.105,
                0.524,
                0.872,
                0.621
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "One important check consists in verifying that the sum of this flow must be equal on assets and liabilities sides. This is the case with a total of 3040. If the payment of the dividends would have been translated at Year 2 average rate, for sure we would have found a mistake already in the statutory cash flow statement which would have been carried over in the consolidated cash flow statement."
        }
